response.original_title: Dir En Grey - TOUR23 PHALARIS -Vol.II- ｢a knot｣ LIMITED 25TH ANNIVERSARY LIVE
response.overview: The live footage for the “「a knot」 LIMITED 25TH ANNIVERSARY LIVE” from “TOUR23 PHALARIS -Vol.II-“, held at KBS Hall on May 5th will be released as DIR EN GREY Official Fan Club 「a knot」 only item in October 2023. It includes all the songs performed that night, focused on the songs from the 11th ALBUM “PHALARIS”, to “JEALOUS” and “惨劇の夜 (Sangeki no Yoru)”, which were performed to celebrate this special night marking the 25th anniversary of the Official Fan Club 「a knot」.
response.title: Dir En Grey - TOUR23 PHALARIS -Vol.II- ｢a knot｣ LIMITED 25TH ANNIVERSARY LIVE
